prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and charming flat 2D botanical illustration for a greeting card front. In the center, a cartoon-style illustration of Lao Lao and Jordan. Jordan is playfully and dramatically presenting Lao Lao with a single, oversized, beautifully detailed tropical leaf instead of a flower bouquet. He holds the giant leaf stem with both hands, offering it with a hopeful, funny expression. Lao Lao is reacting with delighted surprise and laughter, one hand over her mouth. They are both wearing casual, comfortable clothing. The entire scene is framed by a lush, intricate border of various beautifully illustrated botanical elements: monstera leaves, ferns, eucalyptus branches, and small, subtle white blossoms. The background is a soft, solid pastel green color. Centered on the card, below the couple, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, rendered in a dark forest green. The overall style is artistic, clean, and full of personality.
